warning[CS0005]: Using the signal assignment operator `<--` does not constrain the assigned signal.
     /home/tom/development/state-of-zk-security-tools/zksec/bugs/zkbugs/dataset/circom/succinctlabs/telepathy-circuits/trailofbits_prover_can_lock_user_funds_by_including_ill-formed_bigints_in_public_key_commitment/circuits/pairing/fp12.circom:409:17
    
409                  real_out[i][j][idx] <-- out[i][j][idx];
                     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ The assigned signal `real_out[i][j][idx]` is not constrained here.
    
    = Consider if it is possible to rewrite the statement using `<==` instead.
